title: Angelina Jolie's $2M childhood home up for sale!
text:
*Washington D.C., Oct 7 (ANI): Now you can own Angelina Jolie's four-bedroom mid-century modern childhood home in Rockland County, New York as it is up for sale for two million dollars.*
Washington D.C., Oct 7 (ANI): Now you can own Angelina Jolie's four-bedroom mid-century modern childhood home in Rockland County, New York as it is up for sale for two million dollars. The real-estate agent Richard Ellis of Ellis Sotheby's International Realty informed that the 'Maleficent' star's 2 acres NY home is spread on 4,000 square feet and is nestled in rural Snedens Landing on the appropriately named Woods Road, People Magazine reported. He added that the 40-year-old actress lived in the house as a child with her mother and brother, and went to elementary school in Snedens Landing. (ANI) Â»
